name: Namco Transmission Demo Disc v3.2
synopsis: This demo disc contains Namco demos: [[MotoGP 4]], [[Pac-Man World 3]], [[Urban Reign]], [[We Love Katamari]], videos: [[Ace Combat 5: The Unsung War]], Bounty Hounds (PSP), [[Namco Museum 50th Anniversary]], [[Pac-Man World Rally]], Ridge Racer (PSP), [[Tales of Legendia]], [[Tekken 5]], [[Time Crisis 3]], [[Time Crisis: Crisis Zone]], [[Xenosaga Episode II: Jenseits von Gut und Bose]] as well as some game saves.
